{"tid":2329213,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[左膠唔敢出聲系列]巴黎市政府被指僱太多女高層遭中央罰款","createTime":"2020-12-17T05:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T06:13:44.000Z","uid":19365,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c7ccba78d7c727c00a69830639ef9c0f6e88e746","tid":2329213,"uid":19365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:30:03.000Z","msg":"法國首都巴黎市政府因僱用太多女性擔任高層，被中央政府罰款。<br />\n<br />\n巴黎女市長伊達爾戈（Anne Hidalgo）周二（15日）表示，法國公共服務部向市政府罰款9萬歐元（約84.8萬港元），原因是巴黎市政府2018年的管理層16人中，由11名女性和5名男性組成，因女性比例達69%，違反2013年起落實的「管理層中單一性別不可超過六成」的國策。<br />\n<br />\n伊達爾戈形容懲罰決定荒謬、不公和危險，稱法國女性應該獲大幅提升，因為國內仍有很多地方的女性地位大大落後。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eAXBYL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeAXBYL4.jpg&h=f5a89178&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c2a81e852847c62eb3927d79ab797c9bdb825e9","tid":2329213,"uid":36995,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"違反2013年起落實的「管理層中單一性別不可超過六成<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n犯法就係犯法<br />\n咪咁多廢話"},{"pid":"9e3a0afe98c7298a3a6a3f1ba7218be6d13e77ee","tid":2329213,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606795c8f68d09962366485d1cc45ed62964b29f","tid":2329213,"uid":8308,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:52:34.000Z","msg":"D女權就係想100%女高層<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb367dd86de355ec8dba115b3498036f5e1bc96","tid":2329213,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:53:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主幅圖"},{"pid":"e74ad38ff11cefd4bc220eb65f224101022de45b","tid":2329213,"uid":5312,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTi